Dialogue: 2,0:22:05.91,0:22:08.66,Penguin_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}瞳の奥に
Dialogue: 2,0:22:05.91,0:22:08.66,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在你那深邃眼眸中
Dialogue: 2,0:22:11.29,0:22:16.80,Penguin_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}焼き付いた思い出があるだろう
Dialogue: 2,0:22:11.29,0:22:16.80,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}必然有着刻骨铭心的记忆吧
