Dialogue: 2,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.16,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}独自忍受孤独
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.50,0:22:38.55,Penguin_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}何にもなりたくないなんて嘘さ
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.50,0:22:38.55,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说无欲无求 那是骗人的
